1 ingredient cost and the dispensing fee. The pharmacy benefits manager shall also provide the
2 cost that it paid for the specified outpatient prescription drug, including the ingredient cost and
3 the dispensing fee."
4 SECTION 3.5. No later than October 1, 2025, the Department of Insurance shall
5 adopt rules to implement this Part, including rules establishing the pharmacy desert designation.
